    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家交流QQ：300723397</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪简介☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「透明的她与真实的我」是由可味玩企划并发行的一部多角色多结局「超长篇」美少女游戏作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪游戏特色☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·2位可攻略女主角</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·全角色全流程配音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·全程Live2D动画演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·超百万字剧本、百余张CG</strong>（该总数不包括差分）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·精良悦耳的原创音乐</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·独特「实时对话系统」游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪故事缘起☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事是从沪城中一个狭小且不见天日的房间开始的</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宅在家中沉迷二次元且休学了一年的「我」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在监护人妹妹「诗萌」的悉心照料下</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定重返大学生活</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本应于我而言不过是路人般打扮的少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谁知竟在我的眼前出现了———</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG！我看到了CG！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，在本该「两人」的世界中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「三人」的恋爱喜剧就此拉开了帷幕？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪登场角色☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/f192c8bf1164351411e228becd6ef58a.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的妹妹兼监护人，沪城第一女子中学的天才优等生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精通厨艺，爱好时尚。尽管经常和你斗嘴，但依然会一直关心照顾着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自「那时」起，她便发誓要变得足够坚强与优秀，然后换自己来守护曾深受伤害的你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……「已经…没有什么能让我们再分开了，我不允许那种东西存在。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/26425963549bf92d1697731bd49fd23f.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你结识的第一位妹妹之外的异性朋友，沪城普通大学新闻系学生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乖巧内向，极易脸红。为了维持生活与实现梦想，目前在圣火喵喵剧本杀店打工。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >热衷于美少女游戏与乙女游戏，能够轻易察觉到你的二次元浓度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……「世界对着它的孩子，会将它褪色的星星点亮J</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……「如浮跃于穹顶的流彩，将黎明对黑夜的挽歌颂唱」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/dff3bf99ba1d8fcf7c1d96c111b46746.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诗萌的同学兼好友，是有点中二病在身上的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……「我…我我我自然也是深爱着吾之仆从的！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/5e973c4b91ae509d3576e47e7a5112d5.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诗萌的同学兼好友，和小冰似乎有着关系。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >……「就算你是她的哥哥，我也不会轻饶的哟~」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪舞台背景☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/c0751e1948de2e70c3c7e7195aab0cb5.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=169 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/a1666fcb9fdf1d8c72e9691b0649abe5.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=169 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实地取景，还原最真实的「沪城」风光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取景地包括但不限于北外滩、陆家嘴、上海交大、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >市三女中、上海「秋叶原」———</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☪系统☪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/ce77d8cf009c73e1e72251f21aeb36b3.poster.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/ce77d8cf009c73e1e72251f21aeb36b3.webm?t=1772044632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/ce77d8cf009c73e1e72251f21aeb36b3.mp4?t=1772044632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>·Live2D演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全CG全立绘实现Live2D，迈向美少女游戏的次时代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/3847e703b31838c9c4ef231ea40fe7c3.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=168 /></span><strong>·自定义姓名</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的名字，由你来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（*妹妹诗萌会继承玩家自定义的姓氏）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/b72c2a24a53e3da4b281819a97cc6a8b.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=168 /></span><strong>·实时对话</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和美少女对话时保持沉默可不礼貌哦，恋爱冒险远不止简单的选择题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021350/extras/a624bef6588fe3e8a4a00934c35afb71.avif?t=1772044632\" width=600 height=168 /></span><strong>·手机交互</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个人竟然有4个群聊？网络一线牵，珍惜这段缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>声明：本作中的所有角色在游戏剧情发生时均已超过18岁。</strong></p>",
